ZH: 我的祖先是地主。
EN: My ancestors were landlords.

ZH: 在过去的五代，他们家是当地最有钱的地主。
EN: For five generations in the past, their family was the wealthiest landlord in the area.

ZH: 这个村子的地主阶级已经消失了很久。
EN: The landlord class in this village has been gone for a long time.

ZH: 地主把这些土地租给了农民。
EN: The landlord rented out the land to farmers.

ZH: 他们家的土地因为是独特的产权，成为当地比较出名的地主家族。
EN: Their land became famous in the area because of its unique ownership as a landlord family.

ZH: 这个村子的地主非常富有。
EN: The landlords in this village are very wealthy.

ZH: 这片土地曾经是地主的产业。
EN: This piece of land used to be the property of landlords.

ZH: 这个地区的地主统治了几十年。
EN: The landlords ruled this region for several decades.

ZH: 地主家的房屋是最大的。
EN: The house of the landlord's family is the biggest.

ZH: 地主有很多佃户。
EN: The landlord has many tenant farmers.

ZH: 他们拉大banner抗议地主的高租金。
EN: They held up banners to protest against the high rent from the landlord.

ZH: 地主向佃户收取高额租金。
EN: The landlord collects high rent from the tenants.

ZH: 这位地主答应减轻佃户的负担。
EN: The landlord agreed to alleviate the burden of the tenants.

ZH: 地主拥有广阔的土地。
EN: The landlord owns vast tracts of land.

ZH: 地主与农民之间经常发生纠纷。
EN: Disputes often arise between landlords and farmers.

ZH: 这个地主对待佃户非常苛刻。
EN: This landlord treats the tenants very harshly.

ZH: 地主们聚集在一起商议政治事务。
EN: The landlords gathered together to discuss political affairs.

ZH: 地主与农民的关系并不和谐。
EN: The relationship between landlords and farmers is not harmonious.

ZH: 这个地主一直以来都是村子里的领导人。
EN: This landlord has always been a leader in the village.

ZH: 地主在这个地区占据了很多资源。
EN: The landlords have occupied a lot of resources in this region.
